the class was constituted of 3 quizzes and one final take home exam. The final exam was actually easy and quite fun to write, but the small quizzes will be the death of you. teacherRatingTags: ['Graded by few things', 'Beware of pop quizzes', 'Tough grader']

Semester is 3 quizzes, true or false (60%) and 1 takehome exam(40%), which completely diminishes the importance of argumentative politics. AWFUL
I have taken many political science courses with different professors and she is the worst by far! Avoid her! Your gpa will greatly suffer if you take her class!!

rComments: IF you can avoid this class with her, the I suggest you do. Heavy tests and excepts a lot considering she doesn't even explain her powerpoints thoroughly. Premier et dernier cours de politique pris à vie. Prof pas claire qui rend son cours de 2e année aussi difficile qu'un de 4e année. Examens trop long pour le temps alloué. On doit acheter son livre (parlementarisme canadien) et pose des questions très spécifiques pas abordées en classe. Chaque semaine il y a des groupes de discussion et projets.
Elle a complètement détruit tout désir que j'avais d'étudier la politique.

She made the class so much harder and less fun then it needed to be. The textbook you had to buy was the one she wrote and if you didn't have it you could not pass the course. Horrible for french immersion students... would have rather graduated a semester later than taken this class.

Dosent send powerpoints. Her slides are literally copy pasted from her book which she uses as the textbook so ur better off thoroughly memorizing her book. Is rude and dismissive, if your shy dont ask questions she will embarrass you. Her exams are extremely vague and it makes it hard to study for. If this isint a mandatory class DONT!!!

She teaches her class with too many examples of her research and what she believes in as well as having us to buy her textbook that is mandatory. Really tough grader and not willing to help.

Professeure extrêmement engagée dans cours, sans aucun doute. elle est un professeur complètement horrible. Elle est incroyablement biaisée et un évaluateur injuste

1 mid-term exam (easy) + discussion groups + 3% for being present + loud and clear instructions & she gives you past student's works as exemples on how to proceed. Manon est excellente! Elle est tres motivente dans ses cours et encourage la discussion. Le cours était très interessant. Elle est tres severe sur les exemens et les travaux, il faut s'appliquer mais ce n'est pas impossible de bien reussir.

realllly bad teacher!!! shows her opinion way to much. she should probably try and stay more neutral in her lectures. has powerpoints but doesnt put them online so you have to show up for the notes. it all seems really clear till you get to the midtermexam . the class average was a 52! her tests are really hard and and her DGDs annoying!

Une tres bonne professeur. Elle connait tres bien la matiere et on apprend bien dans son cours! J'ai beaucoup aimé sa façon d'enseigner. Le 1er examen est le plus difficile, alors si tu veux faire bien, etudie fort et lis bien tes chapitres le 1er et tu finiras avec A+ dans ce cours!
